data.description: Welcome to the ideal home for your large family – This spacious and thoughtfully designed two-story home is perfect for those who value comfort and functionality.  On the main level, you'll find a versatile study, providing the perfect space for a home office or quiet retreat. The downstairs bedroom is an excellent choice for accommodating guests, offering privacy and convenience. The heart of the home lies in the open living area, where the kitchen seamlessly connects to the living room and dining area, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for family gatherings. The large master bedroom on the second floor is a true sanctuary, featuring a generous walk-in closet and a master bath with double sinks, a tub, a shower, and a private water closet. The second floor also hosts three additional bedrooms, providing ample space for the whole family. The second bathroom boasts dual vanities, a tub/shower combo, and a separate toilet area, ensuring both convenience and comfort for daily routines. Entertainment and relaxation are taken care of with an additional living space upstairs, perfect for a TV room or playroom. With over 2,500 sq. ft. of living space, five bedrooms, and three bathrooms. Gold FORTIFIED Home, Smart Home Technology, with beautiful corner lot and fenced backyard.  **Sellers will provide $5,000 toward rate buydown or closing costs for buyer with acceptable offer.
